data.title: Joan Bennett Service Details - Belleville, Ontario
data.meta_description: For over three generations our family's simple philosophy of dignified service and giving people what they want has made us trusted by more families than any other funeral home in the area. The difference is in the details. Celebrate a lifetime of memories and let us take care of the rest.
